data.description: Pond view on the back of screened patio. Spacious 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms two story townhouse is located in the desirable gated community of Coral Cay Resort. Newly laminate flooring on second floor. No carpet in the house! All fresh painted on all doors and baseboard. First floor offers kitchen, dining and living room combo; a queen size bedroom with full bathroom, laundry closet with stackable washer & dryer. Second floor offers master bedroom with ensuite master bath, bedroom 3 and 4 with one full shared bathroom. The Community includes a resort style swimming pool with kiddie splash pool and spa, a kitchenette for party, fitness room and movie theatre and playground. It is within close proximity to all the theme parks, attractions, restaurants, shopping, major highways, and the Orlando international Airport. This is the perfect for primary residence or investment opportunity.
